        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>June 21</date>
                    <salute>My dear M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Farrer</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>Many thanks. I sh<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>. be an ungrateful dog if I were tired of Orchids, as I owe to them much enjoyment. Nevertheless I confess to an intense hatred for the Bee, Orchid for its anomalous perpetual self-fertilisation.—<ref target="#foot.f2"/></p>
<p>I was aware of wild Ducks sometimes breeding in Trees, as do some other species; but was not at all aware that it was due to compulsion.—<ref target="#foot.f3"/></p>
<p>I have not been well of late, &amp; we are going for a week to London for chance of its doing me good.—<ref target="#foot.f4"/> A little later in summer, I hope that you will able to run down here for a day or two, &amp; I will write again for the chance—<ref target="#foot.f5"/></p>
<p>Yours very sincerely | Ch. Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="tnotes">
                <note xml:id="tnote.n1">1.3 Orchid] <hi rend="italic">interl</hi> </note>
                <note xml:id="tnote.n2">2.3 here] <hi rend="italic">interl</hi> </note>
            </div>

            
            
            
            
            
            
            
